OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fshowers soon fading to leave a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some lengthy clear spells.
OL,8,FTurning chilly with light winds and a
OL,9,Fpatchy frost in prone rural spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FLargely dry and bright,
OL,12,Fafter a chilly start. Cloud increasing
OL,13,Ffrom the west during the late
OL,14,Fafternoon, bringing some outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain across all parts through the
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
